    %% Base images
    UBI9_311["UBI9 Python 3.11<br/>registry.access.redhat.com"]
    UBI9_312["UBI9 Python 3.12<br/>registry.access.redhat.com"]

    UBI9_311 -->|base image| JupyterMinCPU
    UBI9_312 -->|base image| JupyterMinCPU
    UBI9_311 -->|base image| JupyterDS
    UBI9_311 -->|base image| RTMinimal

    %% Build flow
    TektonPipelines -->|builds| Jupyter
    TektonPipelines -->|builds| OtherWB
    TektonPipelines -->|builds| Runtimes
    TektonPipelines -->|publishes to| QuayRegistry["quay.io/modh/*"]

    %% Manifest flow
    ParamsEnv -->|injects digests| BaseKustomize
    CommitEnv -->|injects commits| BaseKustomize
    BaseKustomize -->|included by| AdditionalOverlay
    AdditionalOverlay -->|deployed by| RhodsOperator["rhods-operator"]

    %% Consumers
    RhodsOperator -->|creates| ImageStreams["OpenShift ImageStreams"]
    ImageStreams -->|used by| NotebookController["ODH Notebook Controller"]
    ImageStreams -->|displayed in| Dashboard["ODH Dashboard"]
    Runtimes -->|used by| DSPipelines["Data Science Pipelines"]

